metadata.title: Bogoslof Island Acoustic/Trawl Pollock Survey

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS), Alaska Fisheries Science Center (AFSC), Resource Assessment

metadata.description:
Parameter
number and size of walleye Pollock

Measurement Details
Annual (except 1982) . Assessed by echo integration and mid-water trawling; summer survey

Geographic Area
Bogoslof Island vicinity; Eastern Bering Sea

Publication
various reports available from custodian

[ A TCODE project ]
